<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cullinan Series II Journal — MEEKYNELSON</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS v4 Engine -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <!-- External Custom Stylesheet -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/discover-cullinan.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-[#050505] text-white antialiased selection:bg-neutral-800 selection:text-white">

    <!-- 1. FIXED GLASSMORPHIC NAVBAR -->
    <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full z-50 flex items-center justify-between px-6 md:px-12 py-5 border-b border-neutral-900/40 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-md">
        <button class="md:hidden flex flex-col justify-between h-3.5 w-5 text-white focus:outline-none">
            <span class="w-full h-[1.5px] bg-white"></span>
            <span class="w-full h-[1.5px] bg-white"></span>
            <span class="w-3/4 h-[1.5px] bg-white"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8 text-[13px] font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-neutral-400">
            <a href="index.html" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
            <a href="models.html" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Models</a>
            <a href="rims.html" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Rims</a>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-lg md:text-2xl tracking-[0.35em] uppercase font-bold select-none whitespace-nowrap">
            <h1 class="font-luxury-serif text-white tracking-[0.25em]">MEEKYNELSON</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center text-[12px] md:text-[13px] font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-neutral-400">
            <a href="contact.html" class="transition-colors border border-neutral-800 px-3 py-1.5 md:px-4 md:py-2 hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all whitespace-nowrap">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 2. SYSTEMATIC EDITORIAL HEADER -->
    <header class="pt-40 pb-16 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center md:text-left">
        <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
            <p class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.35em] text-neutral-500 uppercase font-semibold">The Absolute Peak of All-Terrain Luxury</p>
            <h2 class="font-luxury-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl uppercase tracking-widest font-light leading-none">Cullinan Series II</h2>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-neutral-400 font-light leading-relaxed tracking-wide max-w-2xl">
                An analytical breakdown of the updated architecture behind the 2025 manifestation. Urban geometric adaptations outside, combined with microscopic, high-density artistry inside.
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- 3. STAGGERED MASONRY GRID INTRICACIES -->
    <main class="px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto pb-32">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
            
            <!-- Component 1: Exterior Illumination Geometry (Width: 7) -->
            <article class="cullinan-card group md:col-span-7 h-[520px] flex flex-col justify-end p-8 md:p-12">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1632245889029-e406faaa34cd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80" alt="Rolls Royce Front Profile" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover cullinan-img">
                
                <div class="relative z-20 space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-[9px] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-neutral-400 font-medium">
                        <span>Aesthetics Engine</span>
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-neutral-700"></span>
                        <span>01 // Frontal Architecture</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h3 class="font-luxury-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl uppercase tracking-wider text-white cullinan-link inline-block">The Vertical DRL Sequence</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-light max-w-md leading-relaxed">Analyzing the severe vertical daylight running light paths flanking the redesigned lower air intakes, framed alongside an illuminated Pantheon grille layout.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- Component 2: Imperial Interior Digital Horizon (Width: 5) -->
            <article class="cullinan-card group md:col-span-5 h-[520px] md:h-[640px] flex flex-col justify-end p-8">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1617814076367-b759c7d7e738?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="Luxury Cabin Tech" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover cullinan-img">
                
                <div class="relative z-20 space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-[9px] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-neutral-400 font-medium">
                        <span>Digital Horizon Matrix</span>
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-neutral-700"></span>
                        <span>02 // Glass Facia</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h3 class="font-luxury-serif text-xl md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-wider text-white cullinan-link inline-block">The Pillar-To-Pillar Glass</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-light leading-relaxed">An overview of the continuous, dark glass dashboard fascia containing a micro-miniature laser etched canvas, reflecting 7,000 unique star-points alongside the iconic Spirit of Ecstasy clock cabinet.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- Component 3: Placed Leather Artwork (Width: 5 - Desktop Offset Margin) -->
            <article class="cullinan-card group md:col-span-5 h-[460px] flex flex-col justify-end p-8 md:-mt-24">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549399542-7e3f8b79c341?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="Bespoke perforated hide" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover cullinan-img">
                
                <div class="relative z-20 space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-[9px] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-neutral-400 font-medium">
                        <span>Textile Craft</span>
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-neutral-700"></span>
                        <span>03 // Perforated Architecture</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h3 class="font-luxury-serif text-xl uppercase tracking-wider text-white cullinan-link inline-block">Duality Craft Perforations</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-light leading-relaxed">Detailing the brand's abstract cloud patterns, rendered entirely out of 107,000 microscopic perforations meticulously punched into premium grain hides.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- Component 4: Twin-Turbo V12 Engineering Dynamics (Width: 7) -->
            <article class="cullinan-card group md:col-span-7 h-[500px] flex flex-col justify-end p-8 md:p-12">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80" alt="Performance dynamics wheel motion" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover cullinan-img">
                
                <div class="relative z-20 space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-[9px] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-neutral-400 font-medium">
                        <span>Powertrain Baseline</span>
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-neutral-700"></span>
                        <span>04 // 6.75L V12</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h3 class="font-luxury-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl uppercase tracking-wider text-white cullinan-link inline-block">Effortless Uncompromised Power</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-light max-w-md leading-relaxed">Sustaining the hallmark 6.75-liter twin-turbocharged V12 power reserve, calibrated specifically to maintain flat-torque responses across challenging loose-surface topographies.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- 4. LUXURY BRAND FOOTER -->
    <footer class="bg-black text-neutral-600 text-xs py-12 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-neutral-900/50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 text-center md:text-left">
            <p class="tracking-widest font-light text-[11px] uppercase">&copy; 2026 ROLLS-ROYCE MOTOR CARS. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center space-x-6 md:space-x-8 tracking-widest uppercase text-[10px] font-medium">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Legal Notice</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Cookie Settings</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>